Zlatan IbrahimovicLONDON. Figures obtained by journalists in Germany claim to reveal that Manchester United are paying Zlatan Ibrahimovic a salary of more than 19m. The figures, published in a new book called Football Leaks: The Dirty Business of Football, say Ibrahimovic s weekly wage at Old Trafford is 367 600.That is more than double the 165 500 United are paying the world s most expensive player Paul Pogba, according to the same claims.United, who announced an operating profit of more than 37m in their most recent quarterly figures and topped the Deloitte Money League in January, told Sky Sports News HQ they never comment on contract matters . Sky Sports.